Recommended options for this project:

1. MIT License (Recommended)
   - Simple and permissive
   - Allows commercial use, modification, distribution
   - Requires license and copyright notice
   - URL: https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT

2. Apache License 2.0
   - Permissive with patent protection
   - Explicit grant of patent rights
   - Requires license, copyright, and state changes
   - URL: https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0

3. LGPL-3.0
   - Copyleft for library use
   - Allows proprietary use via linking
   - Derivative works must be LGPL
   - URL: https://opensource.org/licenses/LGPL-3.0

STEPS:
1. Choose a license from above (MIT recommended for libraries)
2. Go to https://choosealicense.com/ for full text
3. Replace this file contents with the license text
4. Update the year and copyright holder:
   Copyright (c) 2024 Yurii Dumanskyi
5. Update README.md to reflect the chosen license
6. Uncomment PackageLicenseExpression in Directory.Build.props

